                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Senecaville, Guernsey Co. Ohio</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><date>April 27, 1864</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Much please was<lb/> I a few days since to receive the\n                    <date>April</date><lb/> No. of the Occident. so the Occident intends<lb/> to\n                live another year: it is not one of the<lb/> many things that cannot continue to\n                live in<lb/> these times. The Occident has been coming<lb/> to the wrong Post-Office\n                for some time. Please<lb/> change it from <placeName>Cumberland</placeName> to\n                    <placeName>Seneca=<lb/>ville, Guernsey Co. Ohio</placeName>. I send you the\n                pay<lb/> for the present year.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I thought a year since that I would<lb/> write some articles for\n                you, but I have had<lb/> so many things on hand that it has been<lb/> neglected. I\n                am so constituted that I cannot<lb/> do many things at the same time and do all<lb/>\n                well: perhaps I ought to have written a doubt<lb/> whether I do any one thing very\n                well. I hope<lb/> to prepare some articles this summer which you<lb/> will adjudge\n                appropriate for your magazine.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I wrote an article some time since for<lb/> the <sic>Danvill</sic>\n                Review, a Presbyterian Review<lb/> conducted by ministers and D. D. s in\n                    <placeName>Ken=<lb/>tucky</placeName>, having for its title,—“Experiment<lb/> in\n                Translation of the Talmud.—Valuable<lb/> Things in the Talmud.” My article\n                will,<lb/> I suppose, appear in the <date>June</date> No. The<lb/> Editors have\n                intimated this to me. They express</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p34m91x3t/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
