                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>themselves greatly interested in “the curious and<lb/> useful contents” I\n                    <sic>criticise</sic> some historical<lb/> statements, especially chronological\n                items, pro=<lb/>nouncing them manifestly and mysteriously<lb/> untrue. I mean\n                historical statements in the<lb/> Talmud. I suspect you would not assent<lb/> to\n                some of my criticisms: the testimony of<lb/> history on these points, however,\n                cannot be<lb/> mistaken.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It gives me great pleasure to render<lb/> any help in my power to\n                make the Occident<lb/> an able periodical, well worthy of the patronage<lb/> of the\n                intelligent and religious community.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Yours very truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\"><persName role=\"author\">M. R. Miller</persName>.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
